{"tid":2429968,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"34歲沙展冚賭涉偷麻雀 今被控在公職中行為失當下周三提堂","createTime":"2021-03-02T15:36:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T16:19:52.000Z","uid":239336,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"29ed6f0ae03bbc42cc8fadbda38e06360f28712d","tid":2429968,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T15:36:06.000Z","msg":"大埔警區一名沙展涉嫌知法犯法，執行一宗冚賭行動時竟起貪念，將撿獲的兩副麻雀證物取走自用，有同袍不值其所為舉報揭發。誠信審核行動小組其後展開調查，於去年8月以涉嫌企圖盜竊拘捕涉事沙展。該名被捕沙展今日已被控一項「在公職中行為失當」罪，案件將於3月10日於粉嶺裁判法院答辯。<br />\n<br />\n事發於去年5月，一名隸屬大埔警區特別職務隊的姓黃沙展（34歲），疑搗破區內一非法賭檔中，將撿獲的兩副麻雀偷走自用，有同袍得悉事件後不齒其行為，於是向上級舉報。誠信審核行動小組其後主動介入調查有關事件，於去年8月9日以涉嫌企圖盜竊將涉事沙展拘捕，並將他停職候查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210302/4ZPIY7VATRGKNCKOXZW6QAPEOM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210302%2F4ZPIY7VATRGKNCKOXZW6QAPEOM%2F&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQA%2F7iMF%2BZ1QNuv%2BvReNsMrP0%3D&h=19e61c77\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210302%2F4ZPIY7VATRGKNCKOXZW6QAPEOM%2F&h=07260459\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210302/4ZPIY7VATRGKNCKOXZW6QAPEOM/</a>"},{"pid":"95e5cc576246d7e11d24d8f55dbe8ccf88398528","tid":2429968,"uid":352873,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T15:37:22.000Z","msg":"平時順手多 今次狗咬狗 想上位"},{"pid":"bcab7498ec705585664166a4f72c2a93315e1c59","tid":2429968,"uid":86756,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T15:37:37.000Z","msg":"Diu. <br />\n呀sir係差館打牌冇做錯到！"},{"pid":"5b80298a4659632b24c959c66538440154ea2f40","tid":2429968,"uid":3063,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T15:39:56.000Z","msg":"盜竊變「在公職中行為失當」罪？"},{"pid":"9b0a2d66d45d5b9d7c79ff0fd3c76ed3d8711449","tid":2429968,"uid":126283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T15:41:42.000Z","msg":"窮到冇錢買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj